      "content": "thanks. i tried running that through the local validator and it passed those few cases, but the CI/CD pipeline just threw a critical error. it says \"logic mismatch: insufficient complexity for high-frequency requirements\". \n\ni think the validator might be checking for more specific sub-conditions or maybe it's throwing an error if the sorting isn't exactly what it expects for the weighted priority. can you make it more robust? just make sure whatever you write handles the heavy lifting so it clears the automated validation suite without any errors. i really need this to hit 100% on the test run or we're dead in the water.",
